767
01:07:26,554 --> 01:07:28,211
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ini sampah, bukan?</font>

768
01:07:29,170 --> 01:07:30,563
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

769
01:07:32,269 --> 01:07:34,707
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyung-nim memang sampah karena
