803
01:11:20,809 --> 01:11:23,681
<font color=#FFFF00><i>- Dimana Kim Min Ji?
- Sadarlah, brengsek!</i></font>

804
01:11:23,682 --> 01:11:26,775
<font color=#FFFF00><i>- Apa dia didenda?
